{"tid":1828101,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"浸大: 並非解僱或停職邵家臻","createTime":"2020-01-17T13:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T17:33:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2699fddb471769b132f4c663891a501b2bc3642d","tid":1828101,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:30:24.000Z","msg":"社福界立法會議員邵家臻表示，收到浸會大學的信件，解除他在社會工作系的教學職務。<br />\n<br />\n浸大回覆說，由於有關個案正按既定程序處理，浸大社會科學院成立的審核小組認為，相關教職員未宜執行教學工作，但並非被解僱或停職，基於私穩問題，浸大不便透露個別員工的薪酬安排<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503433-20200117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503433-20200117.htm&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=e8f1ab31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503433-20200117.htm&h=116c161b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503433-20200117.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b216ddf9a090b79140834a112a37dd6379d16f99","tid":1828101,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2638d4ecbfcac6cb9253a0ab0bb645f9b48f75","tid":1828101,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"更生人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1338edcc2df338dd181f6877766ed4c1c5261ee2","tid":1828101,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"成日乜柒都用私隱理由黎擋，如果當事人話唔介意要求校方公開原因咁校方又有乜反應"},{"pid":"ba630927cf19797a089b4ed68304ec6cf0b58803","tid":1828101,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">求下大家<br />\n歐美議員日日講野無人理<br />\n今日好多鬧華為鬧中共tweet響task2呀 <br />\n幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: g